en_2593167_0	16 Bank Accounts in two leading Private Banks in Sri Lanka linked to Former Sri Lankan Ambassador to Russia Udayanga Weeratunga have been frozen based on an order issued by Fort Magistrate Lanka Jayaratne.
en_2593167_1	The Accounts are said to contain a total of 1.5 Million US Dollars.
en_2593167_2	Investigations were conducted by the Police FCID in to the 16 bank accounts linked to Udayanga Weeratunga.
en_2593167_3	The order was issued when the Police FCID informed court about the bank details through a motion.
en_2593167_4	The motion was presented during the court case in to the alleged misappropriating funds by Udayanga Weeratunga through a deal to purchase MiG Fighter Aircraft for the Sri Lanka Air Force during the former administration.
